  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency sass-lint to v1.12.1",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint\">sass-lint</a> from <code>v1.11.1</code> to <code>v1.12.1</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>sasstools/sass-lint</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"1121\">1.12.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/508c135863b408d5dac45a18beccb96c230207ef\"><code>508c135</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;1151 from sasstools/hotfix/use-gonzales-fork</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/9a5196d363f06e6e374ea50c6d68cdf8270da1e1\"><code>9a5196d</code></a> hotfix update gonzales</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/aec4b187c0697366d9d9c7f5ca3a6248ccca9729\"><code>aec4b18</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;1148 from sasstools/v1-dev</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"1120\">1.12.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/07d41dfb326597a6b7fdc727989086458a7f5983\"><code>07d41df</code></a> Merge branch &#x27;develop&#x27; into v1-dev</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/50e21f5a464e51dba371aef15e05d2384a069c24\"><code>50e21f5</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;1123 from sasstools/v1-dev</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/978dbd8a6611ff7bd36c428d13a4d299494cac54\"><code>978dbd8</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;1147 from DanPurdy/feature/prepare-v1-12-0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/b126b4c57b3000b6541a7ed33c5ea15806aeb166\"><code>b126b4c</code></a> :shipit: Prepare v1.12.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/1f2718de1f5f430296ffc64e36429f11eba08a2d\"><code>1f2718d</code></a> :shipit: Prepare 1.12.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/f44a2162251a578d1d857fc5622d1437d9606076\"><code>f44a216</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;1131 from sasstools/feature/ignore-interpolation-class-names</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/24ef9ba97555d6049daf35aec082e52337916e98\"><code>24ef9ba</code></a> Check for non strings for gonales methods</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/241e5a01eed1e15116f721792afb7fa1e6d28318\"><code>241e5a0</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;1144 from occupant/Update-Concentric-property-sort-order</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/4c298460bac1d3c3c8081faadf077ddcee611d3c\"><code>4c29846</code></a> Add updated CSS properties</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/72f4cad72e55d3b2b835d05a7aede1b81dc610aa\"><code>72f4cad</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;1128 from sasstools/feature_update-variable-for-property</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/485a461c72dff45bdd3b1190c15f1d62804ecd60\"><code>485a461</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;1135 from DanPurdy/feature/sasslintrc</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/deabaf663ccd268f8a979ccd4ca995123145d1af\"><code>deabaf6</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;1133 from sasstools/feature/fix-output</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/3b83d6fa7fb0f5b1dea2515c23c2e778310ce3ed\"><code>3b83d6f</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;1132 from sasstools/feature/npm-ignore</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/d977a2fe1cb85dd157e8f9a29418be1f3961d417\"><code>d977a2f</code></a> 📝 Add basic sasslintrc docs</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/554056bc5071f031ca3fe9fbea70117108cdae41\"><code>554056b</code></a> ✅ Fix tests</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/433b57c196af4e21e854b1dfd632c1186d5438f9\"><code>433b57c</code></a> include test files</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/ed93438322dde69522351ec46a3d529a99a6209b\"><code>ed93438</code></a> 🎨 Fix test issues</li>\n<li><a hr