stom properties in declarations</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/e3d0d9aeb994c591381a763764f44a04dd6a3da1\"><code>e3d0d9a</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;1119 from sasstools/feature_update-packages</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/ee8076c7ed81b83f23154222343885fab96d8a87\"><code>ee8076c</code></a> add minimum node version</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sasstools/sass-lint/commit/7a907528e93ccc05f6bdc1cea92c57e2854a6e79\"><code>7a90752</code></a> update all dependencies</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
